hong kong -lrb- ap -rrb- _ prices on the hong kong stock exchange closed sharply higher in moderate trading friday . the blue-chip hang seng index rose 159.17 points , or 1.6 percent , to 9,817.75 . on friday , the index had slipped 3.54 points . turnover amounted to 6.89 billion hong kong dollars -lrb- u.s. dlrs 883 million -rrb- , up from 5.69 billion hong kong dollars -lrb- u.s. dlrs 729 million -rrb- . brokers said share prices slumped in the morning session on profit-taking following recent sharp gains . the key index has gained 25 percent so far this month . prices rebounded late in the afternoon due to futures-related buying , they said . meanwhile , the hong kong association of banks did not announce any further cuts in interest rates at its weekly meeting on friday . last week , local banks announced a 0.25 percentage point cut in interest rates . among properties , cheung kong rose 1.50 hong kong dollars to 50.50 , and sun hung kai properties rose 1.30 dollars to 45.00 . in the banking sector , hang seng bank rose 1.75 dollars to 66.75 , and hsbc holdings rose 1.50 dollars to 182.00 . elsewhere , hutchison whampoa rose 1.10 dollars to 51.00 , and hong kong telecom rose 10 cents to 15.60 . 